## Directory Structure

The names of each folder are intended to be self-explanatory. There are six components organize the inputs and outputs of this project:

1.  [`codebooks`](https://github.com/StefanVermeent/demo/tree/master/codebooks): lists of variable names, labels, and value labels (where applicable).
2.  [`data`](https://github.com/StefanVermeent/demo/tree/master/data): raw data, stored as `.Rdata` and .csv files.
3.  [`manuscript`](https://github.com/StefanVermeent/demo/tree/master/manuscript): a reproducible manuscript for submission to a journal.
4.  [`preregistration`](https://github.com/StefanVermeent/demo/tree/master/preregistration): a preregistration document that details the plans for this project.
5.  [`scripts`](https://github.com/StefanVermeent/demo/tree/master/scripts): R-scripts that read, analyze, and produce all outputs.
6.  [`supplement`](https://github.com/StefanVermeent/demo/tree/master/supplement): a supplemental text with additional information and materials.
